OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Foften large amounts of cloud, but also
OL,7,Fclear spells will occur, which may
OL,8,Fallow some patchy mist or fog to form
OL,9,Fin rural areas later in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FVarying, often large, amounts
OL,12,Fof thin cloud but still bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells will occur. Slightly
OL,14,Fcooler along the coast with onshore
OL,15,Fwinds, becoming very warm or locally
OL,16,Fhot inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
