OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright Saturday, very warm or
OL,7,Flocally hot. Sunday outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fthen scattered showers, breezy and
OL,9,Ffeeling noticeably cooler. Monday
OL,10,Fgenerally dry, with sunny spells and
OL,11,Fvery warm.
